      "title": "Parliament prorogued from midnight today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliament will be prorogued at midnight today (28 July) and the next session will begin at 10.30 am on 03 August 2022 (Wednesday), the Communications Department of Parliament said."
